; costs.test: hledger normalizes a @@ total-cost amount (strips trailing
; zeros), so `@@ $135.00` is stored as mantissa 135 / 0 places; our engine
; keeps the as-written 13500 / 2 places. (The regular `$-135.00` posting
; amount is NOT normalized by either.)
2011-01-01
    a    €100.00 @@ $135.00
    b    $-135.00
